<Layout 
    title="DeJon Gaines | Chief Information Officer" 
    description="Technology executive orchestrating enterprise-scale digital transformations"
>
    <nav>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="nav-content">
                <a href="/" class="logo">DG</a>
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="#about">About</a>
                    <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
                    <a href="#talks">Talks</a>
                    <a href="#writing">Writing</a>
                    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>DeJon Gaines</h1>
                <div class="subtitle">Chief Information Officer</div>
                <p class="tagline">Architecting enterprise technology strategies and digital transformations that scale across healthcare, financial services, and government sectors. Leading innovation in AI implementation, cloud infrastructure, and operational excellence.</p>
                <div class="impact-areas">
                    <span class="impact-item">Digital Transformation</span>
                    <span class="impact-item">AI & ML Implementation</span>
                    <span class="impact-item">Enterprise Architecture</span>
                    <span class="impact-item">Executive Leadership</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-cta">
                    <a href="#about" class="btn btn-primary">About Me</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>About Me</h2>
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="DeJon Gaines" class="profile-image">
                    <div>
                        <p class="section-intro"><strong>Transforming how enterprises adopt and scale technology solutions.</strong> As Chief Information Officer at Conduent, I lead technology strategy for a global customer experience management company with 65,000 employees, 2,000+ enterprise clients, and $3B in annual revenue.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="impact-metrics">
                    <div class="metric-item">
                        <div class="metric-number">$54M</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">Annual Savings Generated</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-item">
                        <div class="metric-number">25K+</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">Associates Impacted</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-item">
                        <div class="metric-number">2,000+</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">IT Professionals Led</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-item">
                        <div class="metric-number">$900M</div>
                        <div class="metric-label">Technology Budget</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>My career has been defined by orchestrating large-scale digital transformations that deliver measurable business impact. From implementing next-generation cloud-based contact center platforms serving 25,000 associates to pioneering real-time AI translation technology, I focus on solutions that create sustainable competitive advantage while generating quantifiable value.</p>
                    
                    <p>I build high-performance teams across multiple geographies, fostering a culture of innovation and accountability. My approach combines deep technical expertise with strategic business acumen—understanding both the technical challenges and the organizational dynamics that make or break technology adoption in large enterprises.</p>
                    
                    <p>Beyond technology leadership, I'm an active voice in the industry through conference speaking and technical writing. I've contributed insights on AI implementation, customer experience transformation, and the evolving role of technology in business operations. I believe the best leadership comes from staying hands-on with emerging technologies while maintaining strategic perspective.</p>
                    
                    <p>Based in Lexington, Kentucky. Graduate of Eastern Kentucky University with executive leadership training from McKinsey & Company.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="experience">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Experience</h2>
                
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>Chief Information Officer</h3>
                    <div class="experience-meta">Conduent · 2020 - Present · Florham Park, NJ</div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Leading technology strategy and digital transformation for a global customer experience management company. Managing $900M technology budget and global team of 2,000 IT professionals.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Designed and implemented next-generation, cloud-based contact center platform revolutionizing operations for 25,000 CX associates</li>
                        <li>Reduced average handle time from 12 minutes to 7.5 minutes through unified customer data access and AI agent assist technology</li>
                        <li>Improved first-call resolution rates by 45% through intelligent routing and contextual customer information</li>
                        <li>Pioneered real-time AI translation technology enabling seamless migration of complex multilingual customer interactions</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>Vice President</h3>
                    <div class="experience-meta">Conduent · 2017 - 2020</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Led enterprise-wide Agile/DevOps transformation, accelerating software deployment time by 60%</li>
                        <li>Designed three-year IT strategic roadmap driving $25M in operational savings</li>
                        <li>Achieved 100% audit compliance while reducing audit preparation time by 50%</li>
                        <li>Drove 100-point increase in Net Promoter Score through data-driven optimization</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>Vice President – IT Service Management</h3>
                    <div class="experience-meta">Xerox Services · 2010 - 2016 · Webster, NY</div>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Achieved 60% reduction in mean time to resolution through standardized incident management</li>
                        <li>Generated $12M in annual cost savings by streamlining IT service delivery</li>
                        <li>Elevated contract renewal rates from 82% to 95%</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>Director – IT Service Management</h3>
                    <div class="experience-meta">Affiliated Computer Services (ACS) · 2004 - 2010 · Dallas, TX</div>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7;">Managed IT operations across multiple delivery centers supporting 15,000 associates.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="talks">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Recent Talks</h2>
                <div class="card-grid">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header">
                            <span class="card-tag">Talk</span>
                            <span class="card-date">2023</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="card-title">Digital Transformation in Customer Experience</h3>
                        <div class="card-event">Genesys Xperience 2023</div>
                        <p class="card-description">Keynote presentation on leveraging AI and cloud technologies to revolutionize customer experience delivery at scale. Explored real-world implementations and lessons learned from managing 2,000+ enterprise clients.</p>
                        <a href="https://www.genesys.com/webinars/large-enterprises-and-outsourcers-going-big-with-genesys-cloud" class="card-link">View Presentation <span>→</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
