                        </div>
                        <h3 class="card-title">Two Years of Generative AI: How Has Customer Experience Delivery Changed?</h3>
                        <div class="card-event">Call Center Times</div>
                        <p class="card-description">Examining the transformative impact of generative AI on customer experience operations, analyzing adoption patterns, implementation challenges, and measurable outcomes.</p>
                        <a href="#https://events.dzone.com/" class="card-link">Read Article <span>→</span></a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header">
                            <span class="card-tag">Article</span>
