            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p class="section-intro">I'm interested in discussing technology leadership opportunities, speaking engagements, or strategic consulting projects. Whether you're looking for guidance on digital transformation, AI implementation strategies, or executive technology leadership, I'd be happy to connect.</p>
